Invocation Name: digits of pi
des:
Develop your math skills by having Alexa recite the digits of pi. She can recite up to 100,000 digits!

Every now and then, Alexa will stop to ask if she should keep going. See if you can get all the way to the end!

To launch, simply say, "Alexa, open digits of pi."
